{"tid":259850,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"on9一問：Windows 10解決咗Ryzen 多線程的問題未？","createTime":"2017-05-27T09:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T07:36:47.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"368281376a2368cd4e42ed604d4baeb4ba6565f9","tid":259850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">發表：2017-03-05 22:59:05<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=455971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60030%26snA%3D455971&d=cD8FHWtypVtjO3z6LyWnWW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5e4a902f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=455971</a><br />\n<br />\nWindows10沒有正確識別Ryzen的CCX架構，猜測每個核心（包括SMT的邏輯核心）都有同樣的L2、L3緩存。也就是說Win10認為Ryzen一共有136MB緩存...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目前Win7測試來看沒有這個問題，遊戲效能比Win10高出17.8%。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n據Reddit用戶稱AMD已經向微軟提交了更新檔，只是尚未被整合/審核通過。<br />\n更新檔會在一個月內放出。順便一提，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Linux早就修復了這個問題</span>。</div>"},{"pid":"7dd608f3bf576d93c491b8232dee1c04102c7587","tid":259850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">發表：2017-05-06 15:14:16<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19017&amp;snA=23526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D19017%26snA%3D23526&d=cD8FHWtypVtjO3z6LyWnWW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=123c51d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19017&amp;snA=23526</a><br />\n<br />\n不久前版中及電腦應用版有人提問新組這顆CPU在打怪上都會有卡頓的情形，然我自己也有這方面困擾，後不斷GOOGLE尋求答案，發現很多文章ryzen多線程上(SMT)關閉，在不少遊戲上表現會比較好，所以引用在黑色沙漠上面，果然有所差別。<br />\n<br />\n很簡單的用MSI Afterburner圖表的FPS比對，主要是看曲線的穩定度，前面為關閉SMT<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201705/f0e0bd4baa19379abe195ef659c3e838.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201705%2Ff0e0bd4baa19379abe195ef659c3e838.JPG&h=b6463b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以看到最小禎的部分明顯拉高，FPS起伏也比較穩定</div>"},{"pid":"a157a539c36ee10168e36523b8b16d830ed7a0af","tid":259850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">發表：2017-05-06 19:43:38<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19017&amp;snA=23526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D19017%26snA%3D23526&d=cD8FHWtypVtjO3z6LyWnWW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=123c51d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=19017&amp;snA=23526</a><br />\n<br />\n#2：<br />\n<br />\n我是說過多線程優化不好..<br />\n不過SMT的關閉與否..<br />\n看似能改善..<br />\n不過這卻是AMD必須要解決的問題..<br />\n<br />\n相較之下..<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Intel並沒有這方面的問題..</span><br />\n多線程優化雖欠佳..<br />\n但是<span style=\"color: violet;\">6核心的平均FPS又比4核心來的好..<br />\n8核心的平均FPS又比6核心來的更好..</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://cheochi2002.myweb.hinet.net/Core%202-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcheochi2002.myweb.hinet.net%2FCore%25202-10.jpg&h=7ed03175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(FPS的表現依照核心數量的提升一點一點地往上增加)<br />\n<br />\n姐係仲未解決？聽講除咗SET高效能之外，閂埋個HPET都有效能提升，HPET係咩嘢嚟，閂咗之後對系統會有咩影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"815d052484a348fbeeb1f101ad69b9cf12becec5","tid":259850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/g6fydzxo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg6fydzxo&h=0b250bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"6765cfa1ebe0b86f